tral bus stand are being prioritized. This initiative aims to find alternatives to property tax increases, with a consultant panel to be formed soon.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/kolhapur-municipal-corporation-plans-five-commercial-complexes-through-public-private-partnership/131630726?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-1574073/131630726.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}]}